casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Larry Gerald MEAD, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 156376
COA: 327881 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 29, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the motion to clarify and/or for rehearing of this Court's April 22, 2019 opinion is considered, and it is DENIED.

CAVANAGH , J., did not participate in the disposition of this case because the Court considered it before she assumed office.
